comments.body:
Was able to confirm issue on Eucalyptus 3.1.2:

{code}
root@euca-10-106-69-137:~# curl http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/block-device-mapping/ephemeral0
sda2
{code}

On AWS, this is what block device mapping is for ephemeral0:

{code}
ubuntu@ip-10-171-42-186:~$ curl http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/block-device-mapping/ephemeral0
/dev/sdb
{code}
